    "description": "Grow your career with Upstox Asia Pacific Associates! We are hiring a Financial Analyst for our Visakhapatnam team. Be part of a workplace that celebrates innovation, diversity, and performance.\n\nAbout Upstox Asia Pacific Associates:\nUpstox Asia Pacific Associates is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Ensure compliance with tax regulations and statutory requirements\n• Liaise with banks, regulators, and financial institutions\n• Implement and maintain internal controls and audit procedures\n• Process payroll and manage employee reimbursements\n• Monitor financial performance against targets and provide variance analysis\n• Maintain general ledger and ensure accurate bookkeeping\n• Manage accounts payable and accounts receivable functions\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Ed / M.Ed from a recognized institution\n• 6-10 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in VBA\n• Proficiency in IFRS\n• Proficiency in Income Tax\n• Proficiency in SAP FICO\n• Proficiency in Python for Finance\n• Proficiency in Due Diligence\n• Proficiency in Tally\n• Proficiency in Risk Management\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Life and accident insurance\n• Salary Range: 12 LPA - 25 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Visakhapatnam, Andhra Pradesh, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Upstox Asia Pacific Associates!",
